  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/89122f95a6f2a7abed19d2533e2780c7.poster.avif?t=1731949456\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/89122f95a6f2a7abed19d2533e2780c7.webm?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/89122f95a6f2a7abed19d2533e2780c7.mp4?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Mushiverse is an online board game that can be played with 4 to 6 players.<br></li><li> With its unique characters, villages, and mechanics, it offers you a one-of-a-kind experience.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/9f3a37083a6aa82bece10d436e4cf485.avif?t=1731949456\" width=624 height=124 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> You can easily defeat your opponents with customized characters.<br></li><li> You can either pay less rent to get ahead, or you can throw your opponents in jail and sabotage them to reach the peak of fun.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/b6092c6cadd8841281c86fd9d78a52f0.poster.avif?t=1731949456\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/b6092c6cadd8841281c86fd9d78a52f0.webm?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/b6092c6cadd8841281c86fd9d78a52f0.mp4?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/f8611f10d04ba9dc06f154ca197886a8.avif?t=1731949456\" width=624 height=124 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> You can annoy your opponents by being a character that goes against the rules of the game. When you select an opponent during the game, you steal their village and character.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/cc0c37c782315ca80c0915f777951e8e.avif?t=1731949456\" width=624 height=124 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> In the Mushiverse universe, each village has its own unique features.<br></li><li> By choosing a village, you select your teammates and determine your strategy.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/af8988f147701b67d812e7532d4e2bc6.avif?t=1731949456\" width=624 height=124 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Earthquake Mechanics</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A randomly selected city is declared as the earthquake city.<br></li><li> The rent multiplier of the earthquake city increases!<br></li><li> Attention! You might want to invest in this city, but an earthquake could happen at any moment!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/9a2649cabe2373a1316ac01efe3576b0.poster.avif?t=1731949456\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/9a2649cabe2373a1316ac01efe3576b0.webm?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/9a2649cabe2373a1316ac01efe3576b0.mp4?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lover Cities</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Two randomly selected cities fall in love with each other.<br></li><li> Any action you take in one love-struck city will automatically be reflected in the other!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/7ff40d5e789870915d53c923b04179cb.poster.avif?t=1731949456\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/7ff40d5e789870915d53c923b04179cb.webm?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/7ff40d5e789870915d53c923b04179cb.mp4?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Farm System</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> If you have at least one house on every property you purchase, you will start earning passive income from that property.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/0d492bd35e85d31f7452d8c28900464f.poster.avif?t=1731949456\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/0d492bd35e85d31f7452d8c28900464f.webm?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/0d492bd35e85d31f7452d8c28900464f.mp4?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/0d39c4f41f32a93dc88aa5dacc19ae24.poster.avif?t=1731949456\" width=624 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/0d39c4f41f32a93dc88aa5dacc19ae24.webm?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032230/extras/0d39c4f41f32a93dc88aa5dacc19ae24.mp4?t=1731949456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
